name: MDE
contents:
<script type="text/javascript">
	// CSS
	if (sap.ui.getCore().byId("exface/vendor/exface/OpenUI5Template/Templates/js/openui5.template.css") === undefined) {
		jQuery.sap.includeStyleSheet('exface/vendor/exface/OpenUI5Template/Templates/js/openui5.template.css', 'exface/vendor/exface/OpenUI5Template/Templates/js/openui5.template.css');
	}
	if (sap.ui.getCore().byId("exface/vendor/bower-asset/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css") === undefined) {
		jQuery.sap.includeStyleSheet('exface/vendor/bower-asset/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css', 'exface/vendor/bower-asset/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css');
	}
	// JS
	jQuery.sap.includeScript('exface/vendor/bower-asset/font-awesome-openui5/dist/font-awesome-openui5.min', 'libs.font_awesome.plugin');
	
	sap.ui.getCore().attachInit(function () {
			sap.ui.jsview("[*alias*].view.[*alias*]", {

			// View has no controller
			getControllerName: function() {
				return null;
			},

			// Instantiate all widgets for the view
			createContent: function(oController) {
				return [
					[!Wayfinder? &startId=`[*id*]` &level=`10` &hideSubMenus=`1`
						 &outerTpl=`@CODE: [+wf.wrapper+]`
						 &innerTpl=`@CODE: [+wf.wrapper+]`
						 &rowTpl=`@CODE: 
							new sap.m.GenericTile({
								header: "[+wf.linktext+]",
								press: function(){sap.ui.core.BusyIndicator.show(0); window.location.href = '[+wf.link+]';},
								tileContent: [
									new sap.m.TileContent({
										content: [
											new sap.m.FeedContent({
												contentText: "[+wf.description+]"
											})
										]
									})
								]
							}).addStyleClass("sapUiTinyMarginBegin sapUiTinyMarginTop tileLayout"),
						 !]
				]}
		});
	});
</script>
